{"id":296247,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-女权工作者叶海燕被拘留引发民间强烈抗/","date":"2013-05-31T16:01:52Z","modified":"2015-03-08T02:10:00Z","title":"维权网 | 女权工作者叶海燕被拘留引发民间强烈抗议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员郑毅报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日</span><span>，广西玉林警方向媒体通报：玉林市博白县警方</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>查处一起故意伤害案，持刀故意伤害</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>名妇女的叶海燕被警方依法行政拘留。此消息立刻成为国内媒体的热点，各大网站也纷纷报道或转载了这一消息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，女权工作者叶海燕等人于本月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日，在海南万宁市第二小学门口，举牌抗议该校校长和一名政府公职人员开房侵害</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>名未成年女生。抗议的牌子上写着：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>校长，开房找我，放过小学生”，并将照片发布到网络上，叶海燕等人的举动引起民间的广泛呼应。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>然而，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>号，当叶海燕刚刚回到广西玉林市博白县租住的房屋之时，租住房子的房东因受到官方压力要求她搬走。当日中午，叶海燕通过微博称，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>人冲进她的房间殴打她，希望大家帮忙报警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>随后，叶海燕在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>人（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>女</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>男）冲进她租住的房子殴打她而自卫之时，被警方强行带走。31日，传出叶海燕被行政拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span><span>各界得知叶海燕竟然被警方以故意伤害他人为由行政拘留后，声援、抗议者众。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>艾未未工作室人员刘艳萍</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/duyanpili\">@duyanpili</a></span><span>在推特上说：陈云飞和叶海燕的遭遇如此相像，先是让房东来赶人，后找男女地痞来围攻殴打，如果不还手，就像陈云飞一样受伤住院，报警无人理睬；如果你还手了，警方会飞速赶来，把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>受伤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>的施暴者送往医院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>治疗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>，然后以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>故意伤害罪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>将你拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>知名学者艾晓明</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/xiaocao07\">@xiaocao07</a></span><span>发布手持一把剪刀，裸露上身，胸前与有“开房找我，放过叶海燕”的照片，并在推特上写道：这是我生过养过的身体，为了叶海燕，我豁出去了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">——</span><span>救救小学生，反抗性暴力！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>正在住医院的人权活动家王荔蕻</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/wlh8964\"><span>@</span><span>wlh8964</span></a></span><span>穿着病号服，手拿一把水果刀，纸牌上写着“校长开房找我，放了小学生！放了叶海燕”。并在电话中哭着对友人说“心里对这个国家绝望了。”</span><span> </span><span>不久前的几天，王荔蕻曾在推特上留言：身体原因，近期将息推、息博。江湖险恶，请大家各自珍重。见谅。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>艾晓明、王荔蕻两位母亲的照片和推文令人动容而悲愤。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在叶海燕刚刚被警方带走之时，著名的维权艺术家艾未未</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/aiww\">@aiww</a>:</span><span>就表示出了极大的担忧：这些年，叶海燕帮助妇女性工作者、艾滋病患者维权，有不少维稳者视她为眼中钉，希望她这次不会被残害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1975</span><span>年出生的叶海燕，自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年开始关注女性尤其是性工作者的人权，并于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年成立了“中国民间女权工作室”，开始为女性维权和预防艾滋病的宣传工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年她在广西的工作室被砸，但她依然坚持关注性工作者的人权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>针对叶海燕的被拘留，民间的质疑不断：冲进叶海燕家中殴打施暴者反而成为受害者，而在家中自卫的叶海燕却因此受到法律的处罚。警方的此举，令人怀疑与叶海燕于本月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日在海南举牌关注未成年女孩受到性侵不无关联，明显是政府对叶海燕进行报复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>注：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23%E5%8F%B6%E6%B5%B7%E7%87%95&#038;src=hash\"><span>#</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">叶海燕</span></span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span>被抓前的录音</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://t.co/tDObWSMhcf\" title=\"http://video.sina.com.cn/v/b/105465934-2416190070.html\"><span><span>http://</span></span><span><span>video.sina.com.cn/v/b/105465934-</span></span><span><span>2416190070.html </span></span><span><span>…</span></span></a></span><span>，此链接已被删除。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ltoiX3yHUkA/Uai3GC5k5GI/AAAAAAAAiwU/-8B83aPMrBY/s1600/BLkqes1CIAEK8St.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"239\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ltoiX3yHUkA/Uai3GC5k5GI/AAAAAAAAiwU/-8B83aPMrBY/s320/BLkqes1CIAEK8St.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>病中的王荔蕻</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qFpUjNqa6wc/UajFVEu8knI/AAAAAAAAixE/AQKM-nf1c6A/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qFpUjNqa6wc/UajFVEu8knI/AAAAAAAAixE/AQKM-nf1c6A/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"229\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>各界网友</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rhF55HM1KB8/Uai3KRfJk1I/AAAAAAAAiws/Or20xnTn1Vo/s1600/BLkWQQ7CIAAymNB.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rhF55HM1KB8/Uai3KRfJk1I/AAAAAAAAiws/Or20xnTn1Vo/s320/BLkWQQ7CIAAymNB.jpg\" width=\"213\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>艾晓明老师 </span><br /><span><br /></span><span><br /></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VS8uOWSIJvA/Uai3IEEpmJI/AAAAAAAAiwk/YlS5pTo-mwY/s1600/image.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VS8uOWSIJvA/Uai3IEEpmJI/AAAAAAAAiwk/YlS5pTo-mwY/s320/image.jpg\" width=\"303\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>叶海燕此前的抗议</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-EgbwiuKqHtI/Uai3KhNKOqI/AAAAAAAAiw0/203KOj5v5z4/s1600/%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-EgbwiuKqHtI/Uai3KhNKOqI/AAAAAAAAiw0/203KOj5v5z4/s320/%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259B%25BE00.jpg\" width=\"315\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>网络消息截图</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[23074,19196]}